OL,3,CSeated yoga group is 'godsend' for
OL,4,Cpeople with neurological conditions
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist Ellis
OL,7,FNordhoff has been hearing how seated
OL,8,Fyoga is helping people with
OL,9,Fneurological conditions.
OL,11,FA seated yoga group has been a
OL,12,F"godsend" for people with neurological
OL,13,Fconditions, and offers a new way to
OL,14,Floosen up and relax.
OL,16,FGentle Seated Yoga at Lytham Methodist
OL,17,FChurch provides all the benefits of
OL,18,Fyoga without the need for complex
OL,19,Fstretches or a mat.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
