OL,3,CSeated yoga group is 'godsend' for
OL,4,Cpeople with neurological conditions
OL,6,FThe group is for everyone, but is
OL,7,Fspecially designed for people with a
OL,8,Frange of conditions including
OL,9,FParkinsons and MS attend.
OL,11,FWhen Sue Monks was diagnosed with
OL,12,FParkinsons, she lost her confidence
OL,13,Fand "felt like everybody was judging
OL,14,Fme."
OL,16,FWith the help of the class, she says
OL,17,Fshe feels like herself again, and
OL,18,F"there's so many nice people and
OL,19,Fthey're so friendly.
OL,21,F"It's been a godsend for me."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
