CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784234869
OL,3,CSeated yoga group is 'godsend' for
OL,4,Cpeople with neurological conditions
OL,6,FYoga teacher Deborah Hopkinson
OL,7,F"welcomes those creaks and cracks" to
OL,8,Fher class. She said: "If you can
OL,9,Fbreathe you can do yoga.
OL,11,F"Anything you can do in yoga can be
OL,12,Fadapted to be done from a seated
OL,13,Fposition in an ordinary chair or a
OL,14,Fwheelchair.
OL,16,F"You don't have to be bendy, you don't
OL,17,Fhave to be really flexible. This is
OL,18,Fwhere we all creak a bit."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
