OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784234869
OL,3,CSeated yoga group is 'godsend' for
OL,4,Cpeople with neurological conditions
OL,6,FWill Nichols used to do lots of manual
OL,7,Flabour but cannot move as well since
OL,8,Fhe was diagnosed with a neurological
OL,9,Fcondition.
OL,11,FThe 83-year-old said: "'My legs have
OL,12,Fgone and they're going to get worse so
OL,13,FI need some form of exercise.
OL,15,F"I've always been fit and able, and
OL,16,Fnow i need to be doing something, so
OL,17,Fthis is ideal."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
