OL,3,CSeated yoga group is 'godsend' for
OL,4,Cpeople with neurological conditions
OL,6,FThe seated yoga classes are offered
OL,7,Feither online or in person, and
OL,8,FDeborah's patience helps put people at
OL,9,Fease.
OL,11,FAll Deborah asks for is a contribution
OL,12,Fto room hire.
OL,14,FSue said: "I didn't think it would
OL,15,Fhelp me as much as it has. It's eased
OL,16,Fmy joints off completely."
OL,18,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,19,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,20,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,21,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
